(deflayer numbers
  _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _       _
  _       S-1     S-4     S-0     S-7     =       S-5     S-6     S-3     S-8     S-4     @eth    _       _
  8       6       4       0       2       S-;     k       3       1       5       7       9
  lsft    _       _       -       _       _       _       j       m       G       b       v       rsft
  @fn     _       _       lmet                    spc                     @num    _
)

(deflayer symbols
